“2. Taking into consideration this universality is established in charter
                            where it has been provided membership open to all peace-loving nations,
                            only condition being members promise fulfil obligations charter;

“5. Taking into consideration advisory opinion ICJ entirely agreement with well known rule of law that it
                            is not possible exercise power discretionally when there are objective
                            facts or rules for exercise such a power;

list.item:
“(1). Declare that judgment of organization on admission new
                                    members ought be based exclusively on juridical conditions
                                    established by Article 4 of charter;
